<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>HYROX // 12-Week Plan</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:wght@300;400;500&family=DM+Sans:wght@300;400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root {
    --black: #0a0a0a;
    --white: #f5f2ed;
    --orange: #e8521a;
    --grey: #1e1e1e;
    --mid: #2e2e2e;
    --muted: #888;
    --green: #4caf79;
    --blue: #4a9eff;
    --yellow: #f5c842;
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  body { background: var(--black); color: var(--white); font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif; min-height: 100vh; overflow-x: hidden; }

  header {
    padding: 20px 20px 14px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mid);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    position: sticky; top: 0;
    background: var(--black);
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .logo { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 26px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--orange); }
  .logo span { color: var(--white); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-left: 8px; opacity: 0.45; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; }
  .race-badge { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--orange); background: rgba(232,82,26,0.1); border: 1px solid rgba(232,82,26,0.25); padding: 5px 11px; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }

  .tabs { display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mid); overflow-x: auto; scrollbar-width: none; background: var(--black); }
  .tabs::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }
  .tab { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; padding: 13px 20px; cursor: pointer; color: var(--muted); border-bottom: 2px solid transparent; white-space: nowrap; transition: all 0.2s; background: none; border-left: none; border-right: none; border-top: none; outline: none; }
  .tab:hover { color: var(--white); }
  .tab.active { color: var(--orange); border-bottom: 2px solid var(--orange); }

  main { max-width: 760px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 16px 80px; }
  .section { display: none; }
  .section.active { display: block; }

  .overview-hero {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a0f08 0%, #1c1c1c 60%, #0a0a0a 100%);
    border: 1px solid var(--mid);
    border-left: 3px solid var(--orange);
    padding: 28px 24px;
    margin-bottom: 22px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .overview-hero::before { content: 'HYROX'; position: absolute; right: -8px; top: 50%; transform: translateY(-50%); font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 90px; color: rgba(232,82,26,0.05); letter-spacing: 4px; pointer-events: none; }
  .hero-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .hero-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 40px; letter-spacing: 2px; line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .hero-sub { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.6; max-width: 460px; }

  .stats-row { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 1px; background: var(--mid); border: 1px solid var(--mid); margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .stat-box { background: var(--grey); padding: 16px; text-align: center; }
  .stat-num { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 30px; color: var(--orange); line-height: 1; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .stat-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; }

  .section-title { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 20px; letter-spacing: 2px; margin-bottom: 14px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .section-title::after { content: ''; flex: 1; height: 1px; background: var(--mid); }

  .phase-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 10px; margin-bottom: 22px; }
  .phase-card { border: 1px solid var(--mid); background: var(--grey); padding: 18px; cursor: pointer; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .phase-card:hover { border-color: var(--orange); }
  .phase-header { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; align-items: flex-start; margin-bottom: 6px; }
  .phase-name { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .phase-weeks { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; }
  .phase-desc { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; margin-bottom: 10px; }
  .phase-focus-tags { display: flex; gap: 6px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .tag { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; }
  .tag.orange { background: rgba(232,82,26,0.14); color: var(--orange); }
  .tag.blue { background: rgba(74,158,255,0.14); color: var(--blue); }
  .tag.green { background: rgba(76,175,121,0.14); color: var(--green); }
  .tag.yellow { background: rgba(245,200,66,0.14); color: var(--yellow); }

  .tracker-card { border: 1px solid var(--mid); background: var(--grey); overflow: hidden; margin-bottom: 14px; }
  .tracker-header { padding: 12px 16px; background: rgba(232,82,26,0.07); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mid); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--orange); }
  .tracker-row { display: flex; align-items: center; padding: 11px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(46,46,46,0.5); gap: 12px; }
  .tracker-row:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .tracker-metric { flex: 1; font-size: 13px; }
  .tracker-value { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); }
  .tracker-input { background: var(--black); border: 1px solid var(--mid); color: var(--white); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 12px; padding: 5px 10px; width: 90px; border-radius: 2px; outline: none; transition: border-color 0.2s; text-align: center; }
  .tracker-input:focus { border-color: var(--orange); }
  .tracker-unit { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); width: 40px; }

  .week-selector { display: flex; gap: 5px; flex-wrap: wrap; margin-bottom: 8px; }
  .week-btn { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 1px; padding: 6px 11px; border: 1px solid var(--mid); background: var(--grey); color: var(--muted); cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.15s; border-radius: 2px; outline: none; }
  .week-btn:hover { border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--white); }
  .week-btn.active { background: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--white); }
  .week-btn.completed { opacity: 0.55; }
  .week-btn.completed::after { content: '✓'; margin-left: 3px; }

  .day-grid { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; }
  .day-card { border: 1px solid var(--mid); background: var(--grey); overflow: hidden; transition: border-color 0.2s; }
  .day-card:hover { border-color: rgba(232,82,26,0.4); }
  .day-header { display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; padding: 13px 16px; cursor: pointer; user-select: none; }
  .day-left { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 12px; }
  .day-dot { width: 7px; height: 7px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; }
  .dot-strength { background: var(--orange); }
  .dot-run { background: var(--blue); }
  .dot-hybrid { background: var(--yellow); }
  .dot-rest { background: var(--muted); }
  .day-name { font-family: 'Bebas Neue', sans-serif; font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; }
  .day-type { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; margin-top: 1px; }
  .day-right { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .day-duration { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); }
  .complete-btn { width: 22px; height: 22px; border: 1.5px solid var(--mid); border-radius: 50%; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; cursor: pointer; transition: all 0.2s; flex-shrink: 0; background: none; color: transparent; font-size: 11px; outline: none; }
  .complete-btn:hover { border-color: var(--green); color: var(--green); }
  .complete-btn.done { border-color: var(--green); background: var(--green); color: var(--black); }

  .day-body { display: none; padding: 0 16px 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--mid); }
  .day-body.open { display: block; }
  .workout-block { margin-top: 12px; }
  .workout-label { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--orange); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 7px; }
  .exercise-list { list-style: none; display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 5px; }
  .exercise-list li { font-size: 13px; color: var(--white); padding-left: 14px; position: relative; line-height: 1.4; }
  .exercise-list li::before { content: '—'; position: absolute; left: 0; color: var(--muted); font-size: 10px; top: 2px; }
  .note-block { margin-top: 10px; padding: 9px 12px; background: rgba(232,82,26,0.06); border-left: 2px solid var(--orange); font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); line-height: 1.5; }

  .phase-label-sm { font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 2px; color: var(--muted); text-transform: uppercase; margin-bottom: 14px; margin-top: -2px; }

  .progress-bar-wrap { background: var(--mid); height: 5px; border-radius: 3px; margin-bottom: 7px; overflow: hidden; }
  .progress-bar-fill { height: 100%; background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--orange), #ff8f60); border-radius: 3px; transition: width 0.4s ease; }
  .progress-meta { display: flex; justify-content: space-between; font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 10px; color: var(--muted); letter-spacing: 1px; margin-bottom: 18px; }

  .checklist-item { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 11px; padding: 11px 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--mid); cursor: pointer; user-select: none; transition: background 0.15s; }
  .checklist-item:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .checklist-item:hover { background: rgba(255,255,255,0.02); }
  .check-box { width: 17px; height: 17px; border: 1.5px solid var(--mid); border-radius: 2px; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 2px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; transition: all 0.2s; font-size: 10px; color: transparent; }
  .checklist-item.checked .check-box { background: var(--orange); border-color: var(--orange); color: var(--white); }
  .check-text { font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.4; }
  .check-text small { display: block; font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 2px; }

  .bottom-nav { display: none; position: fixed; bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0; background: var(--grey); border-top: 1px solid var(--mid); z-index: 200; }
  .bottom-nav-inner { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; }
  .bnav-btn { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; justify-content: center; padding: 9px 4px; gap: 3px; cursor: pointer; background: none; border: none; color: var(--muted); font-family: 'DM Mono', monospace; font-size: 9px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-transform: uppercase; transition: color 0.2s; outline: none; }
  .bnav-btn.active { color: var(--orange); }
  .bnav-btn svg { width: 19px; height: 19px; }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .tabs { display: none; }
    .bottom-nav { display: block; }
    main { padding-bottom: 88px; padding-top: 14px; }
    .stats-row { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
    .hero-title { font-size: 32px; }
  }

  @keyframes fadeUp { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); } }
  .section.active > * { animation: fadeUp 0.28s ease both; }
  .section.active > *:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.05s; }
  .section.active > *:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.08s; }
  .section.active > *:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.11s; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="logo">HYROX <span>MIXED // 12 WKS</span></div>
  <div class="race-badge" id="countdown-badge">LOADING</div>
</header>

<div class="tabs">
  <button class="tab active" onclick="showSection('overview',this)">Overview</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showSection('plan',this)">Training</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showSection('progress',this)">Progress</button>
  <button class="tab" onclick="showSection('prep',this)">Race Prep</button>
</div>

<main>

  <!-- OVERVIEW -->
  <div class="section active" id="section-overview">
    <div class="overview-hero">
      <div class="hero-label">12-Week Program</div>
      <div class="hero-title">Mixed Hyrox<br>Training Plan</div>
      <div class="hero-sub">Beginner–intermediate athlete. 5 days/week. Strength and running focused, with Hyrox-specific conditioning built progressively through Phases 2 and 3.</div>
    </div>

    <div class="stats-row">
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">12</div><div class="stat-label">Weeks</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">5</div><div class="stat-label">Days/Week</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num">8</div><div class="stat-label">Stations</div></div>
      <div class="stat-box"><div class="stat-num" id="days-done-count">0</div><div class="stat-label">Days Done</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Program Structure</div>
    <div class="phase-grid">
      <div class="phase-card" onclick="goToPlan(1)">
        <div class="phase-header"><div class="phase-name">Phase 1 — Foundation</div><div class="phase-weeks">Weeks 1–4</div></div>
        <div class="phase-desc">Build aerobic base and establish lifting patterns. Low intensity, high consistency. Running volume introduced progressively.</div>
        <div class="phase-focus-tags"><span class="tag orange">Strength Base</span><span class="tag blue">Aerobic Running</span><span class="tag green">Movement Quality</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-card" onclick="goToPlan(5)">
        <div class="phase-header"><div class="phase-name">Phase 2 — Build</div><div class="phase-weeks">Weeks 5–8</div></div>
        <div class="phase-desc">Raise intensity. Introduce Hyrox-specific movements — sled, wall balls, burpee broad jumps. Longer runs and heavier lifts.</div>
        <div class="phase-focus-tags"><span class="tag orange">Progressive Overload</span><span class="tag yellow">Hyrox Stations</span><span class="tag blue">Threshold Running</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="phase-card" onclick="goToPlan(9)">
        <div class="phase-header"><div class="phase-name">Phase 3 — Race Ready</div><div class="phase-weeks">Weeks 9–12</div></div>
        <div class="phase-desc">Race simulation. Combine running and stations under fatigue. Taper in Week 12. Peak for race day.</div>
        <div class="phase-focus-tags"><span class="tag yellow">Race Simulation</span><span class="tag green">Speed Work</span><span class="tag orange">Taper</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Weekly Structure</div>
    <div class="tracker-card">
      <div class="tracker-header">How your 5 days are split</div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Monday</div><div class="tracker-value" style="color:var(--orange)">Strength — Lower Body</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Tuesday</div><div class="tracker-value" style="color:var(--blue)">Run — Aerobic / Intervals</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Wednesday</div><div class="tracker-value" style="color:var(--orange)">Strength — Upper Body</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Thursday</div><div class="tracker-value" style="color:var(--yellow)">Hybrid — Conditioning + Hyrox</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Friday</div><div class="tracker-value" style="color:var(--blue)">Run — Long / Tempo</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Sat / Sun</div><div class="tracker-value">Rest + Recovery</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- TRAINING -->
  <div class="section" id="section-plan">
    <div class="section-title">Week <span id="current-week-label">1</span></div>
    <div class="week-selector" id="week-selector"></div>
    <div class="phase-label-sm" id="week-phase-label"></div>
    <div class="day-grid" id="day-grid"></div>
  </div>

  <!-- PROGRESS -->
  <div class="section" id="section-progress">
    <div class="section-title">Your Progress</div>
    <div class="progress-bar-wrap"><div class="progress-bar-fill" id="overall-bar" style="width:0%"></div></div>
    <div class="progress-meta"><span id="progress-text">0 / 60 sessions complete</span><span id="progress-pct">0%</span></div>

    <div class="tracker-card">
      <div class="tracker-header">Benchmark Lifts — Update Weekly</div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Back Squat 5RM</div><input class="tracker-input" type="number" placeholder="—" id="squat" oninput="saveMetric('squat',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">kg</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Deadlift 5RM</div><input class="tracker-input" type="number" placeholder="—" id="deadlift" oninput="saveMetric('deadlift',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">kg</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Push Press 5RM</div><input class="tracker-input" type="number" placeholder="—" id="press" oninput="saveMetric('press',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">kg</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Farmer's Carry</div><input class="tracker-input" type="number" placeholder="—" id="carry" oninput="saveMetric('carry',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">kg/ea</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tracker-card">
      <div class="tracker-header">Running Benchmarks</div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">1km Time</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="t1km" oninput="saveMetric('t1km',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">5km Time</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="t5km" oninput="saveMetric('t5km',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">mm:ss</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">1km Row</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="trow" oninput="saveMetric('trow',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="tracker-card">
      <div class="tracker-header">Hyrox Station PRs</div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Ski Erg 1000m</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="ski" oninput="saveMetric('ski',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Sled Push 50m</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="sled" oninput="saveMetric('sled',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Wall Balls 75 reps</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="wb" oninput="saveMetric('wb',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">Burpee Broad 80m</div><input class="tracker-input" type="text" placeholder="—:——" id="bbj" oninput="saveMetric('bbj',this.value)"><div class="tracker-unit">m:ss</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- RACE PREP -->
  <div class="section" id="section-prep">
    <div class="section-title">Race Day Prep</div>

    <div class="tracker-card" style="margin-bottom:16px;">
      <div class="tracker-header">The 8 Hyrox Stations — Mixed</div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">1 — Ski Erg</div><div class="tracker-value">1,000m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">2 — Sled Push</div><div class="tracker-value">50m (heavier than Open)</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">3 — Sled Pull</div><div class="tracker-value">50m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">4 — Burpee Broad Jumps</div><div class="tracker-value">80m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">5 — Rowing</div><div class="tracker-value">1,000m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">6 — Farmer's Carry</div><div class="tracker-value">200m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">7 — Sandbag Lunges</div><div class="tracker-value">100m</div></div>
      <div class="tracker-row"><div class="tracker-metric">8 — Wall Balls</div><div class="tracker-value">75 reps</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="section-title">Race Week Checklist</div>
    <div class="tracker-card"><div class="tracker-header">Things to handle before race day</div><div id="checklist-container"></div></div>

    <div class="section-title" style="margin-top:20px;">Tactics</div>
    <div class="tracker-card">
      <div class="tracker-header">How to race smart</div>
      <div class="tracker-row" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px;">Start conservative on running laps</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;">Aim 5:30–6:30/km on runs. Mixed sits between Open Women's and Pro Men's pace. Going out hard on Lap 1 destroys you by Station 4.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tracker-row" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px;">Transitions are free recovery</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;">Walk transitions if needed. Station effort should be near max — you recover moving to the next one, not during it.</div>
      </div>
      <div class="tracker-row" style="flex-direction:column;align-items:flex-start;gap:6px;">
        <div style="font-size:13px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:2px;">Wall Balls last — pace them early</div>
        <div style="font-size:12px;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.5;">75 reps unbroken is brutal. Plan for 3 sets of 25 with brief rest. Station 8 is the one most people blow up on — even fresh athletes.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<nav class="bottom-nav">
  <div class="bottom-nav-inner">
    <button class="bnav-btn active" onclick="showSection('overview',this,true)">
